messages: Shower won't turn off water leaking
Is the leak coming from the showerhead itself or from a different part of the shower?
I believe the water is leaking from a different part of the shower, not the showerhead.
Is the water leaking from the shower faucet or the handle?
I think the water is leaking from the shower faucet itself, not the handle.
Is the water leaking constantly, or does it only occur when the shower is turned on?
The water is leaking constantly, even when the shower is turned off.
